证据片段: The specimens used were tubular, 200 mm long, and cut to the length from commercial, unirradiated Zircaloy tubing. Annealed Zircaloy-2 and stress-relieved Zircaloy-4 tubing were produced under standard processes for commercial applications in light-water reactors (LWRs) by Kobe Steel Ltd. and Mitsubishi Metal Corp., respectively.
